# ##Berkeley Mono Stylistic Sets:
# calt: Ligatures
# ss01: Slashed zero (0 with slash)
# ss02: Dotted zero (0 with dot)
# ss03: Gap zero (0 with gap/opening)
# ss04: Slashed zero + slashed 7
# ss05: Dotted zero + slashed 7
# ss06: Gap zero + slashed 7
#
# wght 100-900
# wdth 60-100
# slnt 0 -16
